Subject: Senior Sysadmins Panel
Description: Some say systems administration is a young man's game, and that eventually sysadmins rise into management. They're wrong.  A sysadmin who measures their experience in decades has made mistakes younger sysadmins can't even imagine. This panel lets you learn from their suffering, take advantage of their experience, and laugh at their pain.  Speakers include:Michael W. Lucas, Jeff Marracini, John D. Bell - Track: Tech  - Duration: 50 minutes
